{"tid":1242453,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"政事台？","createTime":"2019-06-19T05:15:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T07:54:02.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ba816f6e9dae60b919b8dc17ae94c36a66bb1ce4","tid":1242453,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:15:25.000Z","msg":"今次運動，泛民好似得鄭松泰，做縮頭龜<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1242002\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1242002</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3b2ac9a8cea4eb9d9730743157e92c3ca1ed00b9","tid":1242453,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba816f6e9dae60b919b8dc17ae94c36a66bb1ce4","tid":1242453,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:15:25.000Z","msg":"今次運動，泛民好似得鄭松泰，做縮頭龜<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1242002\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1242002</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:44:41.000Z","msg":"時事台"},{"pid":"f6b9073b33824ba46e4586b8f176f94562ac53d2","tid":1242453,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:45:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">阻一阻你個post, 有d提議，認同請幫手推post：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n追究 警察濫權濫用武力 先係我地依家既王牌！！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1242366\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1242366</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除左要傾行動細節<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">我覺得星期五 既 主題 應該要集中加強 於</span> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">追究警察濫權濫用武力 ！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">先講建議：</span><br />\n1. 將依項命題提高到 同反送中 一樣高度/重要性！<br />\n2. 老土d, 黎緊日子整多d 中英示威大Banner關於警察濫權、濫用暴力、同醫館局私通 既問題，追究責任！<br />\n3. 議員都應該要有共識去追究依個問題<br />\n4. 加強各種文宣。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">原因：</span><br />\n<br />\n關於行動主題，我地要識得運用火種<br />\n將香港人團怒火keep住燒：<br />\n<br />\n無錯，撤回係未達成，但人人都知個問題，團火已經係白熱化，所以口號照叫，但唔好只集中於依個命題；<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無錯，明日大嶼/雙普選/國歌法都係係大問題，但現實就係依幾個議題好難吸引到大多數市民，太新、太遠，我地可以將佢地加插入我地既討論，但好難成為民意大爆發既火種，只可以乘住其他議題去帶出。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相反地，警察醫館局資料互通、差佬亂打青年人,和平示威者,女示威者、監警會無呀老虎，依d都係實實在在最令市民嬲既議題，亦都係國際社會既人權關注重點，我地一定要將依個命題加強到同反送中一樣高度！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28d1273303c0f2aeba26499ff2a930fbcf859429","tid":1242453,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T07:54:02.000Z","msg":"娛樂台？<br />\n<br />\n民間特首劉德華好耐無蒲頭<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1242797\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1242797</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}